00:00:11.970 --> 00:00:13.346 position:50% align:center line:84%
[SETSUNA]
Let's hear it again!

00:00:13.430 --> 00:00:14.931 position:50% align:center line:84%
[GROUP]
Welcome to the Nijigasaki

00:00:15.015 --> 00:00:16.975 position:50% align:center line:84%
High School Idol Club!

00:00:18.351 --> 00:00:21.021 position:50% align:center line:84%
